query:
INSERT INTO tee_dcap_collateral_certs
                    (serial_number, issuer, sha256, not_after, updated)
                VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, transaction_timestamp())
                ON CONFLICT (serial_number, issuer)
                DO UPDATE SET
                    sha256 = $3,
                    not_after = $4,
                    updated = transaction_timestamp()
